[[File:Armoirie Duc de La Force.svg|thumb]] '''Auguste''' Armand Ghislain Marie Joseph Nompar de Caumont '''de La Force''' (18 August 1878, [[Dieppe, Seine-Maritime|Dieppe]] – 3 October 1961, [[Saint-Aubin-de-Locquenay]]), 12th Duke of La Force, was a French duke and historian. Specialising in the 17th century (he was himself a descendent of the 1000-year-old Caumont de la Force family), his work allowed him to reconstruct events in which his ancestors had taken part. He was elected a member of the [[Académie française]] on 19 November 1925.
